							</div>
							<p class="block-content">spresso 僅有 10 分鐘 ，挑戰最為濃縮與精華的議程，為與會者帶來短而精緻的知識洗禮。</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<Content title="投稿主題範例">
						<ContentFormat>
							<MdContent />
							<Link presentation_content={presentation_content} espresso_content={espresso_content} />
						</ContentFormat>
					</Content>

					<div>
						<Content title="投稿格式"> 各議程類型的投稿格式相同，除標示為公開之資訊會對外公布外，其餘僅供審稿委員於審稿時閱讀。 </Content>
						<FieldDescription title="投稿欄位說明" content={field_content} />
						<PersonalInfo
							title="個人資料"
							description="除了暱稱 / 名字被用於宣傳，其餘資訊僅需提供一人作為代表（當稿件同時有多位講者時），供議程組於聯絡時使用。"
							content={field_content}
						/>
					</div>

					<ContentFormat>
						<MdContent />
					</ContentFormat>

					<QA content={qa_content} />
				</Content>
			</main>
		</div>

		<div class="banner">
			<Banner />
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.main-container {
		max-width: 65rem;
		margin: 3rem auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 5fr;
		grid-template-rows: auto auto;
	}

	.out-container {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		width: 100vw;
	}

	.blocks {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin: 2rem 1rem;
	}

	.block {
		display: block;
		text-align: center;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		padding: 1rem;
		border: 4px solid #86aee5;
		background-color: #fff;
		color: #86aee5;
		align-content: start;
	}

	.block-title {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.block-content {
		word-wrap: break-word;
		text-align: justify;
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.075rem;
	}

	.block-time-spotlight {
		font-size: 5rem;
		font-weight: bold;
	}

	.block-time-normal {
		font-size: 2rem;
	}

	.banner {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	main {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
		padding: 0 3rem;
	}

	.toc {
		padding: 0 2rem;
		justify-self: center;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 900;
	}
</style>
